  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">How We Protect Your Information Company uses commercially reasonable physical managerial and technical safeguards to preserve the integrity and security of your personal information We cannot however ensure or warrant the security of any information you transmit to Company and you do so at your own risk Once we receive your transmission of information Company makes commercially reasonable efforts to ensure the security of our systems However please note that this is not a guarantee that such information may not be accessed disclosed altered or destroyed by breach of any of our physical technical or managerial safeguards</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

